knowledge.title: Zohran Mamdani - Wikipedia
knowledge.content: Zohran Kwame Mamdani[c] (born October 18, 1991) is an American politician who has served as the 112th mayor of New York City since 2026. [d] He is New York's first Muslim and Asian American mayor.
